<p>
Complete this form with information about the property you wish to apply for, the rental broker you are applying to, and your own personal information.</p>
<p>
	This application will be processed for a credit check and viewed by the rental broker and landlord before a decision is made on the status of your rental.
</p>
<hr>
<h1 id="appstitle">Apartment Rental Application</h1>

<%= form_for @r_app, :validate => true do |f| %>
  <% if @r_app.errors.any? %>
    <div id="error_explanation">
      <h2><%= pluralize(@r_app.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this r_app from being saved:</h2>

      <ul>
      <% @r_app.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %>
